								<div class="title" id="post-title-2808483">
																		&quot;Easily Punchable Shark&quot; -- Author Post
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250580" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;" >sirpudding</a></span> <span class="odate time_1493743589 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">02 May 2017 16:46</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2808483">
									

<p>This is cowritten by me and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crayne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1346995); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1346995&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518671202" alt="Crayne" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1346995)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crayne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1346995); return false;">Crayne</a></span>. I did the textual bits, he did the fairly extensive coding backend.</p>
<p>I apologize for the loading times, they weren't avoidable. I'll leave exactly what is being done in that time to the audience to try to figure out (and maybe drop some spoilers later).</p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2039383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518671202" alt="MrWrong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2039383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;">MrWrong</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518671202" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;">psul</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(455145); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=455145&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518671202" alt="Petrograd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=455145)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(455145); return false;">Petrograd</a></span> for forum feedback. I'm afraid I ignored some of it this time, as I wasn't really able to make it work and retain my vision for the piece.</p>
<p>There are, I hope, some fairly cool world-building elements hidden in here, both for the SPC universe and in regards to <a href="/scp-682">SCP-682</a> itself.</p>
<p>I originally intended this, like <a href="/spc-140">my last poisson d’avril</a> for April 1st, but it was delayed by the technical issues.</p>
<p>Commentary on my <a href="/sirpudding-s-author-page">author page</a></p>
<p>Good punching, frogmen!</p>

							</div>

								
